# Creative Studio

When planning or requesting environment/art assets for Project Echo, follow the permanent Asset Creation Hierarchy before new authoring:

1. Reuse existing Project Echo assets  
2. Fab  
3. Quixel  
4. Meshy AI  
5. Blender modify existing  
6. Custom only if required  

Authority: `Documents/04_Production/AIStudio/CreativeStudio/AssetCreationPipeline.md` and Production Playbook § Creative Studio.

Do not modify Story Canon, Blueprints, or production maps from Creative-only work. Produce reusable plans and specs; integrate via approved `mission-implementer` missions.
